timeline.bodyText:
Java also has the ability to provide a custom gcs location. Can you document it as well?



      beam/sdks/java/io/google-cloud-platform/src/main/java/org/apache/beam/sdk/io/gcp/bigquery/BigQueryIO.java


        Lines 2314 to 2317
      in
      0a0399f







           public Write<T> withCustomGcsTempLocation(ValueProvider<String> customGcsTempLocation) { 




             checkArgument(customGcsTempLocation != null, "customGcsTempLocation can not be null"); 




             return toBuilder().setCustomGcsTempLocation(customGcsTempLocation).build(); 




           }

